{"tid":1095761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全校都看她的美胸照　女師不滿被解雇提9千萬賠償","createTime":"2019-04-07T09:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T01:32:58.000Z","uid":32511,"like":552,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"648135b50d2bc8a79642195a24c9a1cf793a762c","tid":1095761,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190404/640_788a8870c790718a4f74032282cd9bf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190404%2F640_788a8870c790718a4f74032282cd9bf6.jpg&h=98f6955b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190404/640_22120c7d87128f196cc01de8e451027b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190404%2F640_22120c7d87128f196cc01de8e451027b.jpg&h=5c87621c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國紐約一名25歲女老師米蘭達(Lauren Miranda)，在2016年拍了一張美胸裸照，私傳給她的男友，但這張裸照之後卻被一名學校學生「獨家取得」導致全校許多同學都看過這張裸照。<br />\n米蘭達因此被學校解雇，但米蘭達認為這件事錯不在她，認為學校處理不公，昨日和律師一起召開記者會，正式對學校提告，並求償300萬美元(約新台幣9千萬元)。<br />\n<br />\n據《美國今日報》報導，米蘭達和男友同在貝爾波特中學(Bellport Middle School)教書，<br />\n米蘭達是一位數學老師，平時教學表現優異。她在2016年於家中臥室，拍了一張美胸裸照送給男友，但最後卻流入學校。米蘭達強調，這張照片當時只傳給她的男友，她不知為何最後會被私給一名學生，然後裸照被流傳開來。<br />\n<br />\n校方最後以「行為不檢、榜樣不佳」為由，將米蘭達開除，但米蘭達相當不滿，她指出這張照片並沒有特意傳給學生，因此沒有違反學校任何紀錄規定。再者，她認為校方有性別歧視，<br />\n她說：「這是我的胸部，是我身體的一部分，我不認為我這樣子做有什麼不對。」律師雷伊(John Ray)也表示，如果今天是男老師拍上空照，就不會覺得有任何問題，「這起事件只是因為發生在一個女人身上，然後她就被開除了」因此米蘭達向校方求償300萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n米蘭達也直呼，自己從18歲起就奉獻給這間學校，但現在只是因為一個無心事件，就這樣被開除，「我的職業、名譽都毀了，已經帶給我難以抹滅的恥辱」。"},{"pid":"7324aa863f3cb1d225766bad9e7f5aa0b8a0f7cd","tid":1095761,"uid":33059,"like":292,"dislike":5,"score":287,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:03:20.000Z","msg":"快d強姦我"},{"pid":"fa073239f477ad6373c328d76bdb24cf78d4ca21","tid":1095761,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfad72c20e85772bacd4d9561c5991f2432db861","tid":1095761,"uid":111270,"like":223,"dislike":3,"score":220,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:04:50.000Z","msg":"好似爭D野"},{"pid":"896fe77cc05e5f3cc199e32bfd05538f4a21d2a3","tid":1095761,"uid":63311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:06:20.000Z","msg":"求原圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07cfd69f5b4a194b8564c7161e06611f3c1171d","tid":1095761,"uid":48609,"like":35,"dislike":3,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:07:24.000Z","msg":"台幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b60a45889934c7dd87631f92f7169c5cff7d03","tid":1095761,"uid":57087,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:07:33.000Z","msg":"真正既美女教師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7ebb82188f96108cf28a3b4d597531a5f40efb","tid":1095761,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:07:57.000Z","msg":"美胸照呢?"},{"pid":"f8bbdec2bd581ff9b2fd6c2681010e5771a7662b","tid":1095761,"uid":81113,"like":238,"dislike":12,"score":226,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/odhUjht.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FodhUjht.png&h=12f3742e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01337644dd52233bf149e4f21f474d2662c97db4","tid":1095761,"uid":19141,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"好明顯佢男友就係佢其中一個學生"},{"pid":"94674825ceadc7e0b9fea5ff1715a1b34e123ce6","tid":1095761,"uid":32511,"like":221,"dislike":15,"scor